<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>PRECIOUS SAVIOUR</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hukdampa lul hun chawian ka,
 Nangmah a mai chuh ka hi;
 Thienna thisan hungtun ziekin,
 Belam No chuh lopi hen!

[V2]
 Lopi, Isu'n ei hukdam hi,
 Amin thieng chuh lopi hen;
 Thienna, thisan hungtun ziekin,
 Hallelujah Belâm No!

[V3]
 2. Chawlhna bukim chuh chang dingin,
 Lunggil in sawttak ka hawl;
 Mahleh ka hawldan chuh nusie'n,
 Gin ziek maiin ka mu tai.

[V4]
 3. Mitphet kal tinin ka ging hi,
 Thisan lul tak hung luong chuh;
 Zie tuikhuk achun ka chawl hi,
 Hukdampa pang chuh belin.

[V5]
 4. Na nasem di'n kikawih chuomin,
 Nanga di'n hingin thing ka;
 Hukdamna bukim leh manbei,
 Kipak takin gen ingka.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>281</hymn_number>
</song>